flowchart LR
  CS[Canonical State] -->|declared canonical input| R[Static Renderer]
  REG[Existing Documentation Registry] -->|projection contract| LC[Existing Document Lifecycle]
  REG -->|renderer identifier, sources, target semantics| R
  CFG[Contract-declared Configuration] --> R
  R -->|text or bytes only| LC
  LC -->|validated plan, lock, atomic write| T[Registered Projection Target]
  WF[Workflow / PR Orchestration] -->|cross-ref serialization and stale-plan guards| LC
  LC -->|findings and bounded records| E[Evidence]
  E -. no runtime authority .-> CS
  CS --> FG[Existing Freshness and Gate Integration]
  REG --> FG
  T --> FG
  T --> C[Bootloader / GUI / LLM / Humans]
  FG -->|accept, warn, or block| C
